&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Times+of+India&amp;rft.atitle=Nuts+about+Natwarlal&amp;rft.date=2018-04-23&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.timescrest.com%2Fopinion%2Fnuts-about-natwarlal-5243&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANatwarlal\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-zn-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-zn_3-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-zn_3-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-zn_3-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://zeenews.india.com/news/delhi/conman-inspired-by-natwarlal-arrested_691648.html\">\"Conman inspired by Natwarlal arrested\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Zee_News\" title=\"Zee News\">Zee News</a></i>. 6 March 2011<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">3 August</span> 2012</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Zee+News&amp;rft.atitle=Conman+inspired+by+Natwarlal+arrested&amp;rft.date=2011-03-06&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fzeenews.india.com%2Fnews%2Fdelhi%2Fconman-inspired-by-natwarlal-arrested_691648.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ANatwarlal\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/?id=VA9TaE2V0eMC&amp;pg=PA22&amp;lpg=PA22&amp;dq=natwarlal+shrivastav#v=onepage&amp;q=natwarlal%20shrivastav&amp;f=false\"><i>Applied Psychology: India Specific and Cross-cultural Perspectives By Smarak Swain</i></a>. p.&#160;22.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=inf